p.note
  | The <code>&lt;i&gt;</code> tag also can be used for emphasizing text in an
  | italic manner, although it is not recommended as <code>&lt;em&gt;</code>
  | should be used. However, the <code>&lt;i&gt;</code> tag can still be used to
  | define text in an alternative voice or mood.

h3 Bold

p
  | The <code>&lt;strong&gt;</code> tag  and <code>.bold</code> class can be used
  | for emphasizing text with a heavier font-weight.

