h2 Type Colors

p
  | Nobody constantly wants black text on a white background, do they? Of course not.
  | That's why Concise comes with various classes that can be used to change the
  | color of text.

p.note
  | You can change the <code>$colors</code> map in the
  | <code>/custom/_globals.scss</code> file to adjust any of the base
  | colors or add your own colors. Any color added will automatically have an
  | appropriate <code>.text--*</code> and <code>.bg--*</code> class created for it.
